lish'`, `None` | Whether to remove standard English stopwords |\n| `max_features` | `30 000`, `50 000` | Vocabulary size cap |\n\n`RandomizedSearchCV` with `n_iter=30` and 3-fold CV gives a good cost-quality trade-off compared to exhaustive grid search.","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"search_params = [\n    {\n        'preprocess__tfidf__ngram_range' : [(1, 1), (1, 2), (2,2)],\n        'preprocess__tfidf__max_df' : [0.7, 0.9,],\n        'preprocess__tfidf__min_df' : [5, 10, 15],\n        'preprocess__tfidf__stop_words' : ['english', None],\n        'preprocess__tfidf__max_features' : [30000, 50000],\n    }\n]\n\nrs = RandomizedSearchCV(\n    estimator = sgd_model,\n    param_distributions = search_params,\n    scoring = 'f1_macro',\n    n_iter = 30,\n    n_jobs = -1,\n    cv = 3,\n    verbose = 1,\n    random_state = 42\n)\n\nrs.fit(X_train, y_train)","metadata":{"trusted":true,"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2026-03-22T01:44:39.426998Z","iopub.execute_input":"2026-03-22T01:44:39.427585Z","iopub.status.idle":"2026-03-22T02:09:52.156491Z","shell.execute_reply.started":"2026-03-22T01:44:39.427553Z","shell.execute_reply":"2026-03-22T02:09:52.155266Z"}},"outputs":[{"name":"stdout","text":"Fitting 3 folds for each of 30 candidates, totalling 90 fits\n","output_type":"stream"},{"execution_count":117,"output_type":"execute_result","data":{"text/plain":"RandomizedSearchCV(cv=3,\n                   estimator=Pipeline(steps=[('fe',\n                                              FunctionTransformer(func=<function feature_engineering at 0x7b79dc1fdee0>)),\n                                             ('preprocess',\n                                              ColumnTransformer(transformers=[('tfidf',\n                                                                               TfidfVectorizer(max_df=0.7,\n                                                                                               min_df=5,\n                                                 